Name: Dungeon Chest
About the game: Dungeon Chest is an old-school puzzle game. You play as a young man who has recently learned the exciting legend of the Treasure of Akzbezth. Eager to obtain the many riches undoubtedly stored within, he travels to South America to enter an ancient Inca dungeon where the treasure is said to be hidden. However, he may soon find that it will not be as easy as he thought. Features: Charming pixel graphics. Fun puzzles. More than 100 rooms. Simple gameplay Note: 10% of the net revenue earned from this game goes to the World Monuments Fund.
